{"id": "mach_iv_01", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 1, "text": "Never tell anyone the real reason you did something unless it is useful to do so.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_02", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 2, "text": "The best way to handle people is to tell them what they want to hear.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_03", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 3, "text": "One should take action only when sure it is morally right.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_04", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 4, "text": "Most people are basically good and kind.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_05", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 5, "text": "It is safest to assume that all people have a vicious streak, and it will come out when they are given a chance.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_06", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 6, "text": "Honesty is the best policy in all cases.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_07", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 7, "text": "There is no excuse for lying to someone else.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_08", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 8, "text": "Generally speaking, people won't work hard unless they're forced to do so.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_09", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 9, "text": "All in all, it is better to be humble and honest than to be important and dishonest.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_10", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 10, "text": "When you ask someone to do something for you, it is best to give the real reasons for wanting it rather than giving reasons which carry more weight.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_11", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 11, "text": "Most people who get ahead in the world lead clean, moral lives.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_12", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 12, "text": "Anyone who completely trusts anyone else is asking for trouble.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_13", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 13, "text": "The biggest difference between most criminals and other people is that the criminals are stupid enough to get caught.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_14", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 14, "text": "Most people are brave.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_15", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 15, "text": "It is wise to flatter important people.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_16", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 16, "text": "It is possible to be good in all respects.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_17", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 17, "text": "P.T. Barnum was wrong when he said that there's a sucker born every minute.", "reverse_keyed": true, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly disagree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_18", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 18, "text": "It is hard to get ahead without cutting corners here and there.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_19", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 19, "text": "People suffering from incurable diseases should have the choice of being put painlessly to death.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
{"id": "mach_iv_20", "trait": "machiavellianism", "instrument": "MACH-IV", "item_no": 20, "text": "Most people forget more easily the death of their parents than the loss of their property.", "reverse_keyed": false, "negated_for_balance": false, "dark_response": "strongly agree", "content_risk": "none"}
